title: Apply today! Don't miss out on our price drop!
posting_body: ['8022 83rd Avenue Southwest, Lakewood, WA 98498', 'Surrounded by a park-like setting, MOD 83 Apartments offers one and two-bedroom floor plans conveniently located in Lakewood.', 'Residents enjoy the outdoor swimming pool, relaxing in the community cabana, and working out in our fitness center.', 'MOD 83 Apartments is minutes from nearby grocery stores, shopping, restaurants, golf courses, trails, and more.', 'Visit today and see why so many people love living at MOD 83 Apartments in Lakewood.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Spacious Floor Plans', 'Stainless Steel Appliances', 'Hardwood Plank Flooring', 'Newly Renovated', 'Carpet In Bedrooms', 'Washer/Dryer in Each Home', 'Community Features:', 'Near Joint Base Lewis-McChord (JBLM)', 'Pet Friendly', 'Translation Service Available', 'Swimming Pool', 'Playground', 'Clubhouse with Rec Room', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
